quran[74]{c,v,t}:
  56,1,“Chikadzachitika chochitikacho (Qiyâma)
  56,2,“Palibe wotsutsa za kuchitika kwake
  56,3,“Chidzatsitsa (oipa) ndi kutukula (abwino)
  56,4,“Nthaka ikadzagwedezeka kwamphamvu
  56,5,“Ndipo mapiri akadzaperedwaperedwa
  56,6,“Nkukhala fumbi longouluka
  56,7,"“Choncho, inu mudzakhala m’magulu atatu (kulingana ndi zochita zanu)"
  56,8,“Anthu akumanja (abwino;) taonani kukula kwa ulemelero wa anthu akumanja
  56,9,“Ndi anthu akumanzere (oipa;) taonani kuipa khalidwe la anthu akumanzere
  56,10,“Ndipo otsogola (pochita zabwino pa dziko) adzakhalanso otsogola (polandira ulemu tsiku lachimaliziro)
  56,11,“Iwowo ndioyandikitsidwa (kwa Allah)
  56,12,“M’minda yamtendere
  56,13,"“(Iwowo oyandikitsidwawo), gulu lalikulu lochokera kumibadwo yakale"
  56,14,“Ndipo ochepa ochokera ku mbadwo wotsirizira
  56,15,“Uku ali m’makama (m’mabedi) olukidwa ndi zingwe zagolide
  56,16,“Atatsamira m’makamawo uku akuyang’anizana (mwachikondi)
  56,17,“Anyamata osasintha adzakhala akuwazungulira iwo (ndi kuwatumikira)
  56,18,"“Uku atatenga matambula ndi maketulo (odzaza ndi zakumwa za ku Jannah), ndi zipanda zodzaza ndi zakumwa zochokera mu akasupe oyenda"
  56,19,“(Zakumwa zake) zosapweteketsa mutu ndiponso zosaledzeretsa
  56,20,“Ndi zipatso (zamitundumitundu) zimene azikazisankha
  56,21,“Ndi nyama yambalame imene mitima yawo izikafuna
  56,22,“Ndi akazi ophanuka maso mokongola
  56,23,“(Kukongola kwawo) ndiye ngati ngale zosungidwa bwino mzigoba zake
  56,24,“Kukhala mphoto chifukwa cha zimene amachita (zabwino padziko lapansi)
  56,25,“M’menemo sakamva mawu achabe ngakhale (mawu a) machimo
  56,26,"“Koma mawu oti: “Mtendere! Mtendere!”"
  56,27,“Anthu akudzanja lamanja. Taonani kukula malipiro a anthu akudzanja lamanja
  56,28,“(Adzakhala m’mithunzi ya) mitengo ya masawu yopanda minga
  56,29,“Ndi mitengo ya nthochi yobereka kwambiri
  56,30,"“Ndi m’mithunzi yotambasuka kwambiri, yosachoka"
  56,31,“Ndi madzi oyenda mosalekeza
  56,32,“Ndi zipatso zambiri
  56,33,"“Zopezeka mnyengo zonse, ndiponso zosaletsedwa (kwa amene akuzifuna)"
  56,34,“Ndi zoyala zapamwamba (zawofuwofu)
  56,35,“Ndithu tidzawalenga (akazi okhulupirira) m’kalengedwe kapamwamba
  56,36,“Tidzawapanga kukhala anamwali
  56,37,“Okondedwa ndi amuna awo; ofanana misinkhu
  56,38,“A anthu akudzanja la manja
  56,39,“Gulu lalikulu lochokera ku m’badwo woyamba
  56,40,“Ndiponso gulu lalikulu lochokera ku mibadwo yotsiriza
  56,41,“Anthu akudzanja lakumanzere. Taonani chilango choopsa kwa anthu akudzanja lakumanzere
  56,42,“Adzakhala mu mvuchi wamoto ndi m’madzi owira
  56,43,“Ndi mumthunzi wa utsi wakuda
  56,44,“Siwoziziritsa ndiponso siwosangalatsa
  56,45,“Ndithu iwo amakhala kalelo mosangalala (samalabadira kumvera Allah)
  56,46,“Ndipo amapitiriza kuchita machimo aakulu (polinga kuti palibe kuuka ku imfa)
  56,47,"“Ndipo amanena (motsutsa); “Kodi tikadzafa nkusanduka fumbi ndi mafupa ofumbwa, tidzaukitsidwanso?”"
  56,48,““Kodi ndi makolo athu akale (adzaukitsidwanso!)”
  56,49,"“Nena kwa iwo (poyankha kutsutsa kwawo). Ndithudi, amibadwo yoyamba ndi mibadwo yomaliza (omwe inu muli m’gulu lawo)"
  56,50,“Adzasonkhanitsidwa m’nthawi ya tsiku lomwe lakhazikitsidwa
  56,51,"“Kenako inu osokera (njira yachilungamo), otsutsa (za kuuka)"
  56,52,"“Mudzadya (ku Jahannam) mtengo wa Zakkum, (mtengo wowawa wopezeka mu Jahannam)"
  56,53,“Mudzakhutitsa mimba zanu ndi umenewu (chifukwa cha njala yadzaoneni)
  56,54,“(Mkhuto wa mtengowo) adzamwera madzi owira
  56,55,“Adzamwa monga mmene imamwera ngamira yodwala matenda aludzu
  56,56,“Ili ndi phwando lawo tsiku lamalipiro
  56,57,“Ife tidakulengani kodi nchifukwa ninji simukukhulupirira
  56,58,“Tandiuzani za madzi (ambewu ya munthu) amene mumawathira m’chiberekero
  56,59,“Kodi inu ndiamene mumawalenga (madziwo ndi kumayang’anira mkusinthasintha kwake kuti akhale cholengedwa) kapena Ife ndiamene timawalenga
  56,60,“Ife tidalamula imfa pakati panu ndipo Ife sitili wolephera
  56,61,“Kubweretsa ena m’malo mwanu ndi kukulengani mwamaonekedwe ena omwe simumawadziwa
  56,62,“Ndipo ndithu mukdziwa kalengedwe koyamba; nanga bwanji simukukumbukira
  56,63,“Tandiuzani za zimene mukubzala
  56,64,“Kodi ndinu amene mukuzimeretsa kapena ndife Amene tikuzimeretsa
  56,65,“Tikadafuna tikadazitembenuza (mbewu zimenezo kukhala zouma isanakwane nthawi yake yozithyola) choncho mukadakhala mukudandaula
  56,66,"“(Uku mukunena:) “Ndithu ife tangotaya chuma chathu (padera);”"
  56,67,““Koma ife tamanidwa (phindu la khama lathu).”
  56,68,“Kodi mukuwaona madzi amene mukumwa
  56,69,“Kodi ndinu amene mudawatsitsa ku mitambo kapena ndife Amene timawatsitsa
  56,70,“Tikadafuna tikadawapanga kukhala amchere; nanga nchifukwa ninji simuthokoza
  56,71,“Kodi mukuwuona moto umene mumaukoleza
  56,72,“Kodi ndinu amene mudameretsa mitengo yake kapena Ndife tidaipanga
  56,73,"“Ife taupanga kuti ukhale chikumbutso (cha Moto watsiku lachimaliziro akauona), ndikuti ukhale chothandiza kwa anthu apaulendo (amene akuyenda m’chipululu)"
  56,74,"“Choncho, pitiriza kulemekeza dzina la Mbuye wako Wamkulu"